oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn1.powerapple.com/upload/news/article_attachments/file/2016328/1479903064_169913.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.powerapple.com%2Fupload%2Fnews%2Farticle_attachments%2Ffile%2F2016328%2F1479903064_169913.gif&h=ca1eb04f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77eeb8bf1af0d1e921e1baf843ff3bcdf1787f6f","tid":683492,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8edae2765d297a065b1e2467ed414b00a98e5f21","tid":683492,"uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T20:39:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「當時嘅解放軍同依家完全係兩支軍隊，例如話佢哋駕駛技術差係因為冇乜喺城市作戰嘅經驗，都相對可以理解」。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n當年六四班士兵而家都50歲，解放軍仲有咩城市作戰經驗？<br />\n美軍起碼打左伊拉克同派人去敘利亞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"澳門軍事鳩up員黃東？ 收皮啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20151004/00178_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20151004%2F00178_001.html&d=oJS3i7CeAujLbCyY0Sqywdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c4bb5b31\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20151004/00178_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n主力軍備外強中乾「陸戰之王」死火<br />\n<br />\n曾在上月抗戰勝利七十周年大閱兵地面裝備方隊打頭陣的國產「99A坦克」，一向被視為解放軍王牌主力武器，甚至有「陸戰之王」的封號，不過閱兵後卻傳「外強中乾」。內地官媒罕有踢爆，該款國產坦克故障率最高，綵排期間曾死火以及突然誤響起火警報自動停駛，所幸在大閱兵現場未釀事故。而其他被視為先進新型主力裝備，亦被指難以適應高原作戰。<br />\n<br />\n另有官媒日前亦披露，解放軍多款陸軍主戰裝備上月在青海昆侖山舉行演習，但進入海拔四千米以上的高原後，出現各種「高原反應」。從軍方公布圖片顯示，當中亦包括99A坦克。<br />\n<br />\n戰車高原發射失準<br />\n報道指，抵達高原的各款戰車引擎的油溫和水壓容易達到臨界點，戰車屆時啟動保護機制，部件會自動放緩或停止，以致戰車行駛速度下降，甚至自動停車；另外因為戰車未有高原射擊參數，開火時往往會射高等。"},{"pid":"0eaaf3a88f3e00086d6da3870a1e5d156be5d888","tid":683492,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"澳門軍事鳩UP員黃東? 食屎啦死老爺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那殲11與泰國JAS-39C/D模擬單挑 慘遭4：0血洗</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.abc.net.au/news/image/5659238-3x2-700x467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2Fimage%2F5659238-3x2-700x467.jpg&h=dc89b327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕近年來支那不斷積極擴充軍備，尤其在空軍戰力上有長足的進步。但有外媒報導指出，支那於2015年底與泰國進行聯合軍演時，在模擬空戰的項目中，支那殲11-A戰機竟然遭到泰國空軍JAS-39C/D以4:0血洗大敗。"},{"pid":"1e198a212f113a8de3855fbc8b5815c12da82a8c","tid":683492,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf9b5f64e4eb3794626fb505518df35f5257b2f2","tid":683492,"uid":21035,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"8edae2765d297a065b1e2467ed414b00a98e5f21","tid":683492,"uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T20:39:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「當時嘅解放軍同依家完全係兩支軍隊，例如話佢哋駕駛技術差係因為冇乜喺城市作戰嘅經驗，都相對可以理解」。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n當年六四班士兵而家都50歲，解放軍仲有咩城市作戰經驗？<br />\n美軍起碼打左伊拉克同派人去敘利亞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T20:55:54.000Z","msg":"摺被摺到起角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"攞個角隊死人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af0d713b7d48f40aa1920204a4374d881ef3266","tid":683492,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e198a212f113a8de3855fbc8b5815c12da82a8c","tid":683492,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf9b5f64e4eb3794626fb505518df35f5257b2f2","tid":683492,"uid":21035,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"8edae2765d297a065b1e2467ed414b00a98e5f21","tid":683492